#M <ccontavalli at inscatolati.net>
#W mod-xslt
#F trash
#D Generates the configure script needed by mod-xslt
#R autoheader, aclocal, autoconf, rm

#
#   mod-xslt -- Copyright (C) 2002-2008 
# 		 Carlo Contavalli 
# 		 <ccontavalli at inscatolati.net>
